 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-list:l216 level1 lfo255;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span
     style='font-family:"Segoe UI Emoji",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:"Segoe UI Emoji";
     mso-bidi-font-style:italic'>Die <b>Kurvenform</b> ergibt sich aus der
     Kombination von Reaktionszeit (0,3–0,5</span><span style='font-family:
     "Arial",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-style:italic'>&#8239;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Segoe UI Emoji",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:"Segoe UI Emoji";
     mso-bidi-font-style:italic'>s) und Ballgeschwindigkeit (100</span><span
     style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-style:italic'>&#8239;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Segoe UI Emoji",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:"Segoe UI Emoji";
